Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.46,0:00:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 我到底还能做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.31,0:00:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了改变那如狭隘庭园般的现实
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.85,0:00:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.29,0:00:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还活不到人生的一半
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.26,0:00:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反抗 相拥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.83,0:00:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在无意识中被刻上的经验纹身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.30,0:00:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当站在悬崖边的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.47,0:00:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦难抓住了我的手腕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次看到了自己的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.08,0:00:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往更加宽广的领域\N往更深更大的某处
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.19,0:01:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝着无法预测的世界前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.13,0:01:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And lt's calling me again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.84,0:01:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.67,0:11:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是统辖部
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.96,0:11:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第707补给基地，请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.84,0:11:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第707补给基地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.84,0:11:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是联合统辖部，能听到吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.37,0:17:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也无法变回人类
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.87,0:17:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想最后见你一面…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.07,0:01:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.16,0:01:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是绫人君？！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.05,0:02:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫人…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.37,0:02:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心率上升，到达活动临界点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.24,0:02:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C-3向莉丽亚·立特巴克报告
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.45,0:02:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上空的RahXephon放射出gamma射线…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.67,0:02:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云司令让我保管的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.96,0:02:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贰神君…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.34,0:02:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我不叫那个名字了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.55,0:02:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.68,0:02:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你利用M型标本第一号制造出来的…你的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.27,0:02:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名教授
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.25,0:03:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.87,0:03:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,alpha v-1，紧急降落至B甲板
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.54,0:03:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈迪亚特中尉准备使用残存的战斗机再次出击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令，中尉请求许可使用TDD装置
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.46,0:03:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果，等着我的只有你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.06,0:04:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.35,0:04:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达到yólteótl阶段的你的真实形态吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.16,0:04:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dnepr号、Scharnhorst号被击沉！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.16,0:04:38.36,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Dnepr：第聂伯河，欧洲第四大河，全长981公里，流经全乌克兰，南入黑海\NScharnhorst：沙恩霍地斯特号，二战时期的德国海军战列巡洋舰\N满载排水量3.9万吨，舰长230米，航速32节
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.37,0:04:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pernemunde号停止运行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.37,0:04:39.54,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Pernemunde研究所，二战中德国开发出v1、v2飞弹的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.96,0:04:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要放弃！一边后退一边攻击！决不妥协！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.55,0:04:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长，本舰向敌军的中心前进！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.55,0:04:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.55,0:04:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改变航向右转舵6点(67.5度)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.18,0:04:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉，我想赌一赌你的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.35,0:04:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，TDD可以用作武器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.85,0:04:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，不要同归于尽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.98,0:05:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到它面前就立刻释放，好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.86,0:05:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我说“不”呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.77,0:05:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不允许你出击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.44,0:05:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.86,0:05:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，八云司令，我还没有那么愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.16,0:05:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.45,0:05:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.38,0:05:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧，伙计！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.97,0:05:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,alpha 1，起飞！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.55,0:05:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6点方向有D-1！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.06,0:05:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.24,0:05:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿刺场，谐振开启
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.04,0:06:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,场发生器最大功率输出
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.05,0:06:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射偏了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.35,0:06:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别耍小聪明了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.07,0:06:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神啊…神的心脏啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀死浩子的你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.75,0:06:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.96,0:06:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.55,0:06:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人类…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.56,0:07:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.98,0:07:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那里？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.56,0:07:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫人！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.08,0:07:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能…我不会接受的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这种人…你这种人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.96,0:07:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你这种杀死浩子的人！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.85,0:07:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间已到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.56,0:07:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界被声音充满
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.36,0:07:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调律的时刻现在就要来临
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.55,0:08:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫人，怎么了？为什么你这么痛苦？！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.17,0:08:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥，不能再待在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.18,0:08:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.47,0:08:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.34,0:08:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别耍小孩子脾气了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.56,0:08:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总一！一定要回来啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.06,0:08:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,功刀先生…我已经尽力而为了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.57,0:08:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…结果就是这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.28,0:08:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩子，我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.86,0:08:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.96,0:08:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.76,0:09:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了…不行了…！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.27,0:09:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.56,0:09:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金…和你的约定无法兑现了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.28,0:09:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总一！ ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.36,0:09:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些…是我干的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.06,0:09:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些都是我干的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.94,0:09:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，这些就是你做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.66,0:10:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此你还要继续活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.67,0:10:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此你还会继续活下去！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.26,0:10:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了现在，我的乐团指挥的职责也结束了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.35,0:11:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺住！快到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.06,0:11:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个一切都即将改变的世界上…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.15,0:11:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为人类继续活下去，究竟还有多少意义？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.28,0:11:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.36,0:11:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，每一个幸存下来的人都有他应该去做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一点是很清楚的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.37,0:11:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类即使遭遇到这种事情也还是会继续生存下去的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.68,0:11:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在这里啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.68,0:11:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退命令已经下达…虽然命令上是这样说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过看起来无论逃到哪里都是一样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.35,0:11:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有必须去做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.65,0:11:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是你的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.44,0:12:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肮脏的工作就由我接了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.55,0:12:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妨碍我的家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.64,0:12:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鄙视我的家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.85,0:12:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我“D”的家伙都得去死…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.85,0:12:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用力按住！小惠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.65,0:12:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.77,0:13:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.27,0:13:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.24,0:13:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.87,0:13:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.18,0:13:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫人！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.55,0:13:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫人！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.14,0:13:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.98,0:14:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.65,0:14:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.58,0:14:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉丽亚·立特巴克沉没
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.66,0:14:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾尔菲和八云都…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.46,0:14:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你和RahXephon一起消失了，我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.75,0:14:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.76,0:14:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和RahXephon一起在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.77,0:14:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RahXephon在我体内
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.27,0:14:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自身就是RahXephon
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.57,0:14:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.86,0:14:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不再是一个人了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.66,0:14:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.16,0:14:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你…因为你总一他…！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.66,0:15:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把总一还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.97,0:15:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么不死之身，什么玛士撒拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.97,0:15:16.97,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}玛士撒拉(methuselah)：《圣经·创世纪》中人物，据传享年969岁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.76,0:15:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被打中了，还不是会死嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.98,0:15:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.07,0:15:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是D
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.07,0:15:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D是designer's children的D，是Dolem的D
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.16,0:15:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.58,0:15:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.37,0:15:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.37,0:15:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许叫我D…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.17,0:15:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.26,0:16:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且D是表示残次品的D
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你这样的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.37,0:16:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.37,0:16:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧！死吧！去死吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.96,0:16:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.34,0:16:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.56,0:16:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.28,0:16:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.16,0:17:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫人，你真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.04,0:17:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？为什么总一都不放过？ ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.67,0:17:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.34,0:17:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金，抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.26,0:17:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要什么道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.34,0:17:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总一…把我的总一还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.77,0:17:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.85,0:17:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.06,0:17:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照自己的方式继续活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.65,0:17:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不是人类…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.15,0:17:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不再是人类了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.36,0:17:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.95,0:17:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.66,0:17:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么呀？ ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.46,0:17:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是你！是人类！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.96,0:17:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经明白我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.76,0:18:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RahXephon的存在对于我有着什么样的意义…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.64,0:18:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ixtli in yólteótl
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.56,0:18:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去人类心脏的olin
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.27,0:18:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到神的心脏——yólteótl\N接受“真实”的“容颜”——ixtli(伊修特利)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.36,0:18:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫人，和你互补的“另一个你”\N你的“另一半”有了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.45,0:18:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个RahXephon
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.45,0:18:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是将时间物质化，由机械装置构成的神…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.25,0:18:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,众多世界的流浪者…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.88,0:18:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使世界安定、调和的调律者…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.34,0:18:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的歌会使世界融为一体…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.47,0:18:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要恐惧，我的“另一半”啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.47,0:18:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的一切都是你的，你的一切都和我在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.77,0:18:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好活下去，olin
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.24,0:19:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐，请和绫人一起活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.75,0:19:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引导他，把我和你的孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.98,0:19:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听见她的歌了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.65,0:19:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久远，和我有血缘关系的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.57,0:19:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久远
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.07,0:19:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是“另一个你”？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.16,0:19:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的世界和我的世界，谁的世界会…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.95,0:19:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要去！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.75,0:19:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.96,0:19:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很高兴能生而为人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.67,0:19:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用自己的心感受过各种各样的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.76,0:20:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你也相知了两次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.26,0:20:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫人！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.97,0:20:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了，惠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.14,0:20:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了，叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.27,0:20:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了，金
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.85,0:20:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.36,0:20:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.77,0:20:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥，我最喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.57,0:20:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不！不要走！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.24,0:20:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在呼唤我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.84,0:20:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…不能接受…办不到…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.26,0:20:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你…是我唯一爱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.27,0:21:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在等待…这一时刻…这个结局
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.94,0:21:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是多么地令人兴奋和期待啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.76,0:21:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青色的森林之中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.34,0:21:32.35,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}黑曜石之蝶：阿兹特克神话里的女ltzpapalotl
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.34,0:21:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑曜石之蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.26,0:21:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了歌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.57,0:21:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.96,0:23:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重温旧梦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.96,0:23:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打破心的牢笼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.75,0:23:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演奏真实的颜色…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.46,0:23:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终乐章
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.96,0:23:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥和久远的过去与未来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.97,0:23:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界饱含着声音